snippet.title: The Wild at Heart | Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
The Wild at Heart is coming to Xbox on May 20, 2021!

Welcome to the Deep Woods! Get ready to explore a mysterious realm with two precocious kids, magical creatures, and oddball guardians.

Pre-Order TWAH now:https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/p/the-wild-at-heart/9NR8ZBSJQ4FD
